CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 30, 1955, pg. 1 reads: "The Alphas' Cabarama - A happy throng enjoyed the Alpha Phi Alpha's Cabarama last Friday night at the Royal Ballroom. Pictured are some of the tables filled with revelers who enjoyed the affair. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Women, including one in center wearing dark quilted halter dress, and men, gathered around banquet tables, in the Royal Ballroom for Alpha Phi Alpha Cabarama event
